description:
Headquartered in Geneva Switzerland, WPP Energy GmbH has been in the renewable energy industry since 2009. WPP describes itself as a repository for green energy and environmental technologies which it builds, owns, operates, and maintains. It also licenses technology and enters into strategic joint venture partnerships for the purpose of accelerating the deployment of environmentally friendly technologies.
